Quickstrike:






Quickstrike ducked his head looking at the ground, away from 
Solo. "Quickstrike." he said. He frowned. He dropped down from the 
table he was sitting on, with a sharp clang from his hollow feet. He 
walked to the threshold of the CR room. He looked out into the 
cooridor.
